Cell["\<\
Now any WebGraphics can be rendered on this page, without having to inline \
the runtime in every one. Note however that the stylesheet and script needs \
to be hosted on the same server serving the page otherwise they will get \
blocked by the Content Security Policy (CSP) .\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.990152945992333*^9, 3.9901529818352623`*^9}, {
   3.990166290020308*^9, 3.990166327136407*^9}, {3.9901853803474817`*^9, 
   3.99018544741462*^9}, 3.9903739748029137`*^9},
 CellID->33358824,ExpressionUUID->"29ba5801-0f7f-4511-8b5d-ac7972162f47"],

